{"tid":2259767,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「罪名不成立，當庭釋放」 她哭得崩潰了","createTime":"2020-10-27T05:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T09:11:05.000Z","uid":32473,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"54d4a2ae2787c3017fc65f8d2c947388a07e07b5","tid":2259767,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:27:13.000Z","msg":"係立場睇到既手足被控有攻擊武器<br />\n審兩日拖左一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BD%AA%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B-%E7%95%B6%E5%BA%AD%E9%87%8B%E6%94%BE-%E5%A5%B9%E5%93%AD%E5%BE%97%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0%E4%BA%86/?fbclid=IwAR2vaCXEsWSyxTwKDPqkItw4ORJs6mUVf6-Q9Qf7XMX4ibifnEtaYgZKaHQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E9%2587%258B%25E6%2594%25BE-%25E5%25A5%25B9%25E5%2593%25AD%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25B4%25A9%25E6%25BD%25B0%25E4%25BA%2586%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2vaCXEsWSyxTwKDPqkItw4ORJs6mUVf6-Q9Qf7XMX4ibifnEtaYgZKaHQ&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETUigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=e3b544cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%25AB%258B-%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E9%2587%258B%25E6%2594%25BE-%25E5%25A5%25B9%25E5%2593%25AD%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%25B4%25A9%25E6%25BD%25B0%25E4%25BA%2586%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2vaCXEsWSyxTwKDPqkItw4ORJs6mUVf6-Q9Qf7XMX4ibifnEtaYgZKaHQ&h=c79ebd3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%BD%AA%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B-%E7%95%B6%E5%BA%AD%E9%87%8B%E6%94%BE-%E5%A5%B9%E5%93%AD%E5%BE%97%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0%E4%BA%86/?fbclid=IwAR2vaCXEsWSyxTwKDPqkItw4ORJs6mUVf6-Q9Qf7XMX4ibifnEtaYgZKaHQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n翌日，裁判官作出裁決，批評兩名警員在處理及記錄證物做法粗疏與欠缺專業，包括警員 A 沒有將證物處理事宜記錄在警察記事冊內，直至事發後八個月才在口供中補寫證物，違反《警察通例》第 53 條；後來他在補寫的口供中出現兩大錯誤 &mdash; 將接收證物的警員身分寫錯，並漏寫了重要證物鐳射筆，但警員 A 見到重大錯誤後，沒有在第二份口供中解釋出錯原因，直至在庭上被追問時，他才首次披露將證物處理事宜寫在私人記事簿上，但其上司及控方大律師毫不知情，裁判官指有關做法有違常理、不盡不實。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警員 B 沒有正當存放證物入證物袋，而是存放在私人儲物櫃達五個多月，而他在檢閱證物後更沒有在警察通用的資訊系統記錄，違反《警察通例》第 30 條；警員 B 直至今年 7 月 1 日才錄取第一份口供，並表示自己參考了去年 11 月 9 日的五項文件，但當時有關文件根本未出現。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官把判詞讀到這裏時，全法庭依然寂靜無聲，就等待以下這段裁決：舉證責任在於控方，證物處理在普通法為重要一環，但在此案中因警員的疏忽不當，令法庭不能確定證物沒有受到不當的干擾，亦未能確定證物是被告身上的物品，故裁定被告罪名不成立，當庭釋放。一聲「COURT」之後，旁聽席上的公眾拍掌歡呼，纖瘦的她仍只懂呆站。"},{"pid":"9ece3efa559ff5f9ed42deaf4e0579eb053d4709","tid":2259767,"uid":32473,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:28:32.000Z","msg":"有時真係諗<br />\n好彩果兩隻狗咁撚蠢<br />\n有時呢啲位真係好講運氣<br />\n邊諗到會有狗戇鳩到將證物放係自己locker"},{"pid":"7f858233f448a90b2f920e4a4bd9d7dc8f152a26","tid":2259767,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87932f4f42335bda79969d93d7fb63870762d9c7","tid":2259767,"uid":32473,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7f858233f448a90b2f920e4a4bd9d7dc8f152a26","tid":2259767,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T05:31:54.000Z","msg":"話果日位女手足喊到飛起<br />\n連身邊男旁聽師都忍唔住流眼淚<br />\n比單案精神折磨左一年<br />\n最後因為黑警戇鳩先可能打得甩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=